Kvkbd - A virtual keyboard for X11 based on Qt
==============================================

Dependencies:
	- Qt4 or Qt5 (QtWidgets and QtX11Extras needed for Qt5)
	- libxtst (X11 Record extension library)

On Debian systems, this can be installed with:

Qt5:
	$ sudo aptitude install qtbase5-dev qtbase5-dev-tools qt5-qmake libqt5x11extras5-dev libxtst-dev

Qt4:
	$ sudo aptitude install libqt4-dev qt4-dev-tools qt4-qmake libxtst-dev

Build instructions:

Qt5:
	$ qmake -qt5
	$ make -kj$(nproc)
	$ sudo make install

Qt4:
	$ qmake -qt5
	$ make -kj$(nproc)
	$ sudo make install
